<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7732275>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–11. Leptomastix baspinari sp. n. Holotype female (figs 1–6): dorsal habitus (1), lateral habitus (2), antenna (3), forewing (4), mesosoma (5), ovipositor (6). Paratype female (figs 7–9): lateral habitus (7), ovipositor (8), antenna (9). Male (figs 10–11): aedeagus (10), antenna (11)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7732275/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

